defaultdue to 
defaulta reduction in hospital admission rates
default. NICE have endorsed EiP as a proven case study for QIPP. NICE concluded that the programme scored 100% for evidence of change and 75% fo
defaultr both savings made and quality.
default 
defaultThis approach e
defaultnabl
defaulted
default the delivery of higher standards of care at
